        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Ba<add>?</add></placeName>
                <date>4. Nov: 1847</date>.</p>
            <p>My dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">The package containing the Occident<lb/> I have recd. It has been
                determined that <persName>Rehine</persName><lb/> declined going to
                    <placeName>Sea.</placeName> and as the delivery of the<lb/> books will not be
                attended with any inconvenience<lb/> so far as I can see for the present, continue
                to<lb/> send them to me and I will have them<lb/> distributed. With regard to the
                collections due<lb/> you from subscribers that <hi rend="underline">may</hi>
                interfere with<lb/> his avocations but if not he shall do that<lb/> also until you
                make other arrangements.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I see <persName>Block</persName> has commenced and I think<lb/> if
                he will persevere attentively, and not<lb/> aspire too high, he may succeed it is
                his<lb/> last and best resort and I hope he will<lb/> regard it so. Indeed the death
                of <persName>Miss<lb/> Aguilar</persName> does send a chilling pain to my
                heart.<lb/> She was a model of adornment <del>
                    <add>?</add>
                </del> to<lb/> our faith and I trust her admirers will<lb/> immortalize her memory
                in each congregation<lb/> in this country by erecting a monument<lb/> and placing
                it, if not in, at least about its<lb/> entrance to each <sic>shoole</sic>. Who would
                hesitate<lb/> to subscribe? none. do let it be accomplished.</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>Your excursion to the north I hope has realized<lb/> all you could desire. Your
                health requires your absence occasionally.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mrs. Cozen</persName><lb/> kind remembrance is fully<lb/>
                reciprocated and I wish her health was<lb/> equal to mine. mention me kindly to
                the<lb/> family. and accept for yourself the best<lb/> wishes of my heart.</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Very sincerely</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">Yrs</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <persName role="author">Dan. Judah</persName>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
